text: The Tour Bohemia was a one-day cycling race held annually between 2012 and 2014 in the Czech Republic. It was part of UCI Europe Tour in category 1.2. It was replaced in 2015 by the East Bohemia Tour. ==Winners== ==References== Category:Cycle races in the Czech Republic Category:Recurring sporting events established in 2012 Category:2012 establishments in the Czech Republic Category:Recurring sporting events disestablished in 2014 Category:2014 disestablishments in the Czech Republic Category:UCI Europe Tour races Category:Defunct cycling races in the Czech Republic
